head: 3. Classify points on maps
inf1: Two methods are available - template matching and filtering.
inf2: Template matching used the same approach as for clipping maps from images. Here, the templates are symbols extracted from legend elements, which should be saved in /templates/symbols/, see the point 1 on the app
threshold: Threshold (for symbol detection with template matching)
inf4: You can find the marked points on the maps in /data/output/maps/align/
